    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you\u2014this car is a total gem! It\u2019s in truly pristine condition and has been babied since day one. It looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. If you've been looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new and ready for the open road, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great home!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
